name: Cosmo Moon and Sky Floor Lamps with Polished Stainless Steel
description: The Cosmo Sky and Cosmo Moon floor lamps by Kifu Paris are whimsical and sculptural pieces, inlaid in bronze-patina brass and each with a beautiful parchment or shell inlaid piece. The amorphous shapes are an abstract and poetic reinterpretation of a star-filled cosmic sky.
